			BBox 0 get BBox 1 get moveto
			BBox 2 get BBox 0 get sub 0 rlineto
			0 BBox 3 get BBox 1 get sub rlineto
			BBox 2 get BBox 0 get sub neg 0 rlineto
			closepath
			clip
